n hover:underline focus:underline">median </a>or Q2=E2=80=94marks the 50th =
percentile of the data set. It divides the second quarter of your data from=
 the third quarter. It also divides your data into two equal groups: the bo=
ttom 50 percent and the top 50 percent.
</p><h3 class=3D"
