        col-span-10 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-6 md:col-start-2 lg:col-start=
-3
      " id=3D"section-calculate-quartiles-using-excel-or-google-sheets">Cal=
culate Quartiles Using Excel or Google Sheets
</h3><p class=3D"text-grey col-span-10 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-6 md:col-s=
tart-2 lg:col-start-3">To calculate quartiles in Excel or Google Sheets, us=
e the QUARTILE() function. Because we can use different methods for calcula=
ting quartiles, the results you get from calculating quartiles in Excel or =
Google Sheets may be slightly different than the results you get when calcu=
lating quartiles by hand.
</p><h4 class=3D"
