-3
      " id=3D"section-step-1-find-q1">Step 1 - Find Q1
</h4><p class=3D"text-grey col-span-10 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-6 md:col-s=
tart-2 lg:col-start-3">Suppose your data is in cells A1 through A20. To fin=
d Q1, type: =3DQUARTILE(A1:A20, 1)
</p><h4 class=3D"
       =20
       =20
       =20
        font-light text-[20px] leading-[27px] md:text-[27px] md:leading-[36=
px]
       =20
        col-span-10 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-6 md:col-start-2 lg:col-start=
-3
      " id=3D"section-step-2-find-q2">Step 2 - Find Q2
</h4><p class=3D"text-grey col-span-10 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-6 md:col-s=
tart-2 lg:col-start-3">To find Q2, use the same function, only this time, t=
ype a 2 before the closing parenthesis. Type =3DQUARTILE(A1:A20,2)
</p><h4 class=3D"
       =20
