</p><p class=3D"text-grey col-span-10 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-6 md:col-st=
art-2 lg:col-start-3">Suppose you have your data stored in a variable calle=
d <span class=3D"katex"><span class=3D"katex-mathml"><math xmlns=3D"http://=
