l">x</span></span></span></span>. You can find the three quartiles by typin=
g: QUANTILE(x, probs =3D (0.25, 0.5, 0.75)).=20

</p><p class=3D"text-grey col-span-10 md:col-span-8 lg:col-span-6 md:col-st=
art-2 lg:col-start-3">You can also use the quantile function to find percen=
tiles, deciles, and quintiles.
</p><h2 class=3D"
